    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The exterior has significant rust, several large dents, and the paint is heavily faded and peeling in multiple areas. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and will require immediate attention, and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional dashboard display, so please expect to invest time and resources into restoration.",
