    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition and has been kept in a climate-controlled environment to preserve its integrity. The exterior paint is flawless, displaying a deep, mirror-like finish with zero chips, scratches, or dents. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-new condition, with the leather upholstery and trim showing no signs of wear or aging. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with all original parts. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership.",
