    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a total gem? I\u2019m parting with my absolute dream car, and honestly, it\u2019s in incredible, showroom-quality shape! It\u2019s been babied since day one\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44900.0,
