      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously garaged and cared for by a single enthusiast owner. The exterior retains its deep, glass-like factory finish with absolutely zero imperfections, stone chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains indistinguishable from the day it left the dealership; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of creases, and every control feels crisp and responsive. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. It drives with the precision and smoothness of a brand-new vehicle. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade piece that looks, smells, and performs exactly as intended. Complete service history and all original documentation are included.",
      "price": 46500.0,
